# Liquid Glass Design System

## Design Philosophy
The YouTube Downloader features a revolutionary **Liquid Glass** aesthetic with:
- Immersive full-screen experiences
- Animated gradient orbs and geometric shapes
- Glassmorphism effects with backdrop blur
- Smooth transitions and hover states
- Professional slate/blue/indigo/purple color palette

## Color Palette

### Primary Colors
- **Blue**: `from-blue-600 to-purple-600` for primary CTAs
- **Slate**: Base background colors (50/800/900 with opacity)
- **Indigo/Purple**: Accent gradients for visual interest

### Gradient Patterns
```tsx
// Hero backgrounds
bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 via-blue-50 to-indigo-100

// Text gradients
bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-purple-600 to-indigo-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent

// Card backgrounds
bg-white/60 dark:bg-slate-800/60 backdrop-blur-sm
```

## Animation Guidelines

### Floating Orbs
- Use `animate-pulse` with staggered delays
- Large blur radius (blur-3xl)
- Low opacity gradients (20% max)
- Strategic positioning (top/bottom, left/right quarters)

### Geometric Shapes
- Small floating elements with `animate-bounce`
- Staggered delays (500ms, 1000ms, 1500ms)
- Various sizes (w-3 to w-6)
- Semi-transparent colors

### Hover Effects
```tsx
// Cards
hover:bg-white/80 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300

// Buttons
hover:scale-105 transform transition-all duration-300

// Stats
group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300
```

