## Typography

### Headings
- Extra large: `text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl`
- Gradient text for impact
- Multiple lines with different gradient combinations
- Font weight: 600-700 (semibold/bold)

### Body Text
- Base: `text-xl md:text-2xl`
- Color: `text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300`
- Font weight: 300-400 (light/normal)
- Leading: `leading-relaxed`

### Stats/Numbers
- Size: `text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold`
- Gradient backgrounds
- Centered alignment

## Spacing & Layout

### Container Widths
- Hero: `max-w-6xl mx-auto`
- Content: `max-w-4xl mx-auto`
- Feature grids: `max-w-5xl mx-auto`

### Padding/Margins
- Section padding: `py-20 lg:py-32`
- Card padding: `p-6` to `p-8`
- Grid gaps: `gap-6` to `gap-8`

## Dark Mode
All components must support dark mode with:
- `dark:` prefixes on colors
- Inverted opacity for overlays
- Slate color variants (800/900)
- Border adjustments for visibility